<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0"/>
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no">
<title>领QQ阅读红包</title>
<script>
    document.documentElement.style.fontSize = document.documentElement.clientWidth / 7.2 + 'px';
</script>
<style type="text/css">
	body,p{margin:0;padding:0;}
	img{border:none;}
	a{text-decoration:none;-webkit-touch-callout:none;}
	body{background: #1e1b20;font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-serif;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-webkit-user-select:none;text-align: center;}
	.share img{width: 100%;display: block;}
	.share p{color: #797987;font-size: .26rem}
	.btn{display: block;width: 5.52rem;height: 1.16rem;background:url(images/loadbtn.png) no-repeat;background-size:100% auto;margin:0 auto;-webkit-animation:pop 1s infinite alternate;animation:pop 1s infinite alternate;}
	.sharetit{position: absolute;top:2.64rem;left:0}
	@-webkit-keyframes pop{
		0%{-webkit-transform:scale(1);opacity: .8}
		100%{-webkit-transform:scale(1.06);opacity: 1}
	}
	@keyframes pop{
		0%{-webkit-transform:scale(1);opacity: .8}
		100%{-webkit-transform:scale(1.06);opacity: 1}
	}
	/*弹窗*/
	.mask{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height: 100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);-webkit-align-items:center;-webkit-justify-content:center;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index: 100;display:none;}
	.show{display: -webkit-flex;display:flex;}
	.tiparea{width:6.4rem;background: #fff;border-radius:0.04rem;text-align: center;color: #444;font-size: .28rem;line-height:.4rem;position: relative;}
	.tiparea h3{font-weight: normal;padding:.26rem 0;border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e4e6;font-size: .28rem}
	.tiparea p{padding: 0.64rem 0}
	.btns{display: -webkit-flex;-webkit-flex:1;display: flex;flex:1;width: 100%}
	.btns span{height: 1rem;display: block;width: 100%;line-height: 1rem;-webkit-box-sizing:border-box;box-sizing:border-box;}
	.btns .certain{background: #3d8dcf;color: #fff;}
	.btns .cancle{color: #444;border-top: 0.01rem solid #e3e4e6;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="share">
	<img src="images/sharepic.jpg" alt="领QQ阅读红包">
	<img src="images/sharetit.png" class="sharetit">
	<a href="#" class="btn" id="btn"></a>
	<p>活动仅支持首次安装用户</p>
</div>
<div class="mask">
	<div class="tiparea">
		<h3>下载QQ阅读,畅读海量小说</h3>
		<p>如果还未安装QQ阅读，你可以：</p>
		<div class="btns">
			<span class="cancle">取消</span>
			<span class="certain">下载QQ阅读</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/common.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/zepto-1.1.3.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="share.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://iyuedu.qq.com/event/common/en.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" data-main="http://solomotest4.3g.qq.com/book_res/event/common/ne.js" src="http://solomotest4.3g.qq.com/book_res/event/common/require.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
